description: This file defines the 'Note' entity class used in the backend domain of a note organizer application. It includes properties for note identification, content, associated user, and timestamps.

classes.name: Note
classes.description: Represents a user-created note with properties for ID, title, content, user association, and timestamps.

methods.name: Note()
methods.description: Default constructor initializes the note's ID with a new GUID and sets default values for properties.
